NORTH ATLANTIC.
BERMUDA TO AZORES.
50 FOOT VESSEL FLIPPER 3, WHITE HULL WITH GREEN STRIPE,
ONE PERSON ON BOARD, UNREPORTED BERMUDA (32-18N 064-47W)
TO AZORES (37-44N 025-40W). VESSELS IN VICINITY REQUESTED
